{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_08_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 誰も知らない雲の向こうへ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後　新MVの撮影日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few weeks later‚ on the day of the new music video shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれから瑠依と優で話し合って、瑠依は）\n（音楽番組の最終回に出ることにした訳だが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After Rui and Yu talked it over‚ Rui）\n（decided to appear on the final episode of the music program…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7198406934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "優はグループの将来を見据えて、トリエルのために\nより話題性のある番組に出るべきだと思ってたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ for the sake of the group‚ Yu was thinking you should be on\nthe program that would generate more buzz for TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.459568731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "優も本音では、三人で最終回に出たかったんです\nだけどトリエルのためを思って我慢して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu actually wanted all of us to appear on the final episode together.\nBut she held back for the sake of TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "だから話し合って、優が我慢しなくて済むような\n最高の方法を一緒に考えることにしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we talked it over and decided to work together\nto find the best way so Yu wouldn’t have to hold back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333331425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9910883665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その方法が、三人で最終回を盛り上げて\n特番に負けないくらい世間の話題にすること……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that way is for the three of you to liven up the final episode and\nto make it a hot topic which even can be comparable to the special show……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "最終回に三人で出ると決めてから、優はMVの\nアイデアを出したり、最終回用の企画を考えたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since we decided to appear on the final episode together‚ Yu has been\ncoming up with ideas for the MV and planning things for the final episode…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろと積極的に動いてくれて、裏番組の特番には\n負けないって張り切ってるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s been very proactive‚ and she's been enthusiastic\nto never lose to the special that will be airing at the same time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.2130384207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私が、最終回より特番の方に出るべきだったと\n言われないように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that people won’t say that I should have chosen the special\nover the final episode…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8597973462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "この選択は正しかったと胸を張って言えるように\n最高の最終回にしようと燃えているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ she’s determined to make the best final episode‚\nso she can proudly say that she made the right choice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8333317439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.0737924973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "特番のMCを辞退したことは後悔していないようだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you don’t regret turning down the MC position for the special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0737924973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、しっかり話し合って\n三人で納得して決めましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we had a proper discussion‚\nand the three of us came to an agreement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8000057856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.3390102785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "後悔どころか、優とちゃんとぶつかり合えたことで\n絆がさらに深まった気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Far from regretting it‚ after having that honest confrontation with Yu‚\nI feel like our bond has been stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4666724522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.1652290424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どんなに仲が良くても\n言葉にしなければ伝わらないこともある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how close you are‚\nthere are some things that can’t be conveyed without words…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3666780471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "信頼している相手だからこそ\n時にはぶつかることも必要だったのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the more because you trust each other‚\nmaybe it was necessary to clash sometimes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0666790644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.4334630409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。ぶつかり合って絆がより深まった今なら\n前よりもっといいMVが撮れる気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. Now that our bond has become even stronger after that clash‚\nI feel like we can make an even better music video than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3666775385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "……そろそろ出番ですね。では、行ってきます\n成長した私達の羽ばたきを見ていて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s almost our turn. I’ll be back.\nPlease watch our grown-up wings soar high.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9333442051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9333442051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今日の瑠依は、澄み渡る青空のような\nいい表情をしているな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ Rui has a wonderful expression on her face‚\nlike a clear blue sky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9333487827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "（新しいMVで表現するのは、羽を広げて）\n（未来へ飛翔するTRINITYAiLEの姿……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In the new music video‚ we’ll express the image of TRINITYAiLE）\n（spreading wings and soaring toward the future…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2000134149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "（『les plumes』を初めて歌った時は）\n（まだ未熟で、こんなに高く飛べなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When we first sang “les plumes”‚）\n（we were still immature and couldn’t fly this high.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0666749952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "（沢山の出会いが、経験が、私達の羽を大きくした）\n（沢山の絆が、私達の羽を強くした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Many encounters‚ many experiences‚ have made our wings bigger.）\n（Many bonds have made our wings stronger.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7333335238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "（私一人じゃ、この景色まで辿り着けなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I couldn’t have reached this scenery on my own.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9739585159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（『les plumes』……その羽で）\n（瑠依は俺達にどんな景色を見せてくれるんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（“Les plumes”… with those wings‚）\n（what kind of scenery will you show us‚ Rui?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8333396273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "（この羽なら、どんな未来にも手が届く）\n（この羽があれば、私達はさらなる高みへ羽ばたける）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（With these wings‚ I can reach any future.）\n（By these wings‚ we can soar to even greater heights.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7666688917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "（もっと高く、もっと遠く……）\n（希望の羽で、飛び立とう、目指していこう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Much higher‚ much farther…）\n（with wings of hope‚ let's take off‚ let's aim for it）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.755254658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "（その手をとって連れていくわ）\n（誰も知らない雲の向こうへ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Take my hand‚ let’s go together.）\n（Beyond the clouds‚ where no one knows.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽番組最終回の翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day after the final episode of the music program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.4539761781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 189.9873166323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のゴールデンタイムの視聴率が出たぞ\n視聴率一位だったのは……例の辞退した特番だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ratings for yesterday’s prime-time shows are out.\nThe program that got first place was… the special you turned down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.2000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……。向こうは宣伝にも相当\n力を入れてましたから、この結果も仕方ありませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… They put a lot of effort into advertising‚\nso it’s not surprising that they got those results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.8333335241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そう悲観することもないぞ。トリエルが出演した\n音楽番組は、特番に次ぐ視聴率二位だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be so discouraged. The music program that TRINITYAiLE was on\ngot the second place in the ratings‚ just after the special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.7333335241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "内容もかなり好評で\n最終回にして番組の最高視聴率を更新したらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The content was very well-received‚\nand it apparently broke the program's highest viewership record for the final episode.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.3666668575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "番組が有終の美を飾れたのなら\n私達も頑張った甲斐がありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the program was able to make the grand finale‚\nthen our efforts were worth it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.5000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばSNSでは、最終回とMVの関連ワードが\nトレンドの上位を独占していたそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ I heard that related keywords for the final episode and the MV\nwere dominating the top trending spots on social media.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.8999920528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "話題性なら特番といい勝負だったって\n優が嬉しそうに話してました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu was happily saying that in terms of the topicality‚\nit had been neck and neck with the special show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.9999920528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。大型特番に負けないくらい\n視聴者の心に響いた、いい最終回だったと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. It was a good final episode that\nresonated with viewers‚ which was comparable to the large special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.9999920528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "あと、その特番のプロデューサーから\n瑠依にメッセージを預かっていたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ the producer of that special\nleft a message for you‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.0666658402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "私にですか？　せっかくMCに大抜擢してくれたのに\n断って裏番組に出ましたからね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me? Well‚ Although he handpicked me as the MC‚\nI turned it down and appeared on the competing program…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.4666577022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "自分の選択は後悔していませんが\n恨み言を言われても仕方ありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t regret my choice‚\nbut I wouldn’t blame him if he had complaints.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.6333345413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nどんな内容でも受け入れるので、聞かせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand.\nWhatever the content‚ I’ll accept it. Please tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.566660754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "覚悟は出来ているようだな\nならメッセージを伝えるぞ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem ready.\nThen‚ I’ll tell you the message…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.2333213171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "――新しいMV、とても素晴らしい出来映えで\n改めて天動さんに惚れ込みました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The new music video turned out fantastic.\nI've fallen for you all over again‚ Tendo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.7333457311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "来年も特番をやることになったら\nぜひMCを引き受けていただきたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we do the special again next year‚\nI would love for you to be the MC.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.2999961217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "さらに成長した天動さんに会えるのを\n楽しみにしています……だそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I look forward to seeing you again‚\neven more grown up than you are now… That’s what he said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.2999961217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか\n凄くありがたいお話で、光栄です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see.\nThat’s very kind of him‚ I’m honored.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 303.0333274205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "このメッセージに返信しようと思うんだが\n瑠依から伝言はあるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m thinking about sending him a reply.\nDo you have anything you want to say‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.7332907993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "……では、こう伝えて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Then‚ please tell him this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.5439132765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "目を掛けて下さってありがとうございます\nまた機会をいただけるのであれば、もっと成長して――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your kind attention.\nIf I'm given another opportunity‚ I'll show you how much I've grown――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.9999798455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "アシスタントMCだけでなく、BIG4になった\nトリエルの三人で、番組に出て、歌わせていただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just as an assistant MC‚ but as TRINITYAiLE‚\nall three of us‚ as a part of BIG4‚ to appear and sing on your program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 329.0666505811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "これからのTRINITYAiLEに\n期待していて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please look forward to\nwhat TRINITYAiLE will become.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.2034851343,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}